.TH TIGO 1 "2026-06-15" "tigo" "Tigo Manual"
.SH NAME
tigo \- terminal-based TODO/task management program
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B tigo
[OPTIONS] [\fIroot\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Tigo is a terminal-based TODO/task management program written in Go.
Tasks are stored as \fBTASK.md\fR files inside timestamped directories,
making them grep-able, diff-able, and git-friendly.
.PP
If a \fIroot\fR directory is provided, Tigo uses it as the task database.
Otherwise it looks for a \fB.tigo\fR directory in the current working
directory. If that does not exist, it falls back to
\fB~/.local/share/tigo\fR.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-h, \-\-help
Show the help message and exit.
.TP
.B \-v, \-\-version
Show the version and exit.
.TP
.B \-\-default-config
Print the default configuration to stdout and exit.
.TP
.B \-\-user-config-path
Print the path to the user configuration file and exit.
.SH CONFIGURATION
Tigo loads configuration from YAML files with the following precedence
(highest wins):
.PP
1. \fB.tigo/config.yaml\fR (local, per-directory override)
.br
2. \fB~/.config/tigo/config.yaml\fR (user config, XDG compliant)
.br
3. Built-in defaults
.PP
Configuration options:
.TP
.B sort_by
Sort tasks by \fIid\fR, \fIpriority\fR, \fIdue-date\fR, or \fItitle\fR (default: id).
.TP
.B default_priority
Default priority for new tasks (default: 50).
.TP
.B frame_style
Frame border style: \fIround\fR, \fIdouble\fR, or \fIsingle\fR (default: round).
.TP
.B show_closed
Show closed tasks in the list (default: false).
.TP
.B due_color_enabled
Color due dates by proximity (default: true).
.SH TASK STORAGE
Each task is stored in a directory named \fBYYYYMMDD-HHmmss\fR containing a
\fBTASK.md\fR file. The file format:
.PP
.EX
# Title of the task

- STATUS: OPEN
- PRIORITY: 70
- TAGS: bug, UI
- DUE: 2026-05-11

Description of the task goes here.
.EE
.SH FILES
.TP
\fB~/.local/share/tigo/\fR
Default task database directory.
.TP
\fB~/.config/tigo/config.yaml\fR
User configuration file.
.TP
\fB.tigo/config.yaml\fR
Local per-directory configuration override.
